## üì± MOBILE OPTIMIZATION (Zero Bounce Strategy)

### Performance Targets
- **Lighthouse Score**: 90+ mobile, 95+ desktop
- **Core Web Vitals**:
  - LCP: <2.5s
  - FID (INP): <200ms
  - CLS: <0.1
- **Page Weight**: <500KB initial load
- **Time to Interactive**: <3.5s

### Optimization Tactics
1. **Image Optimization**
   - WebP format with JPEG fallback
   - Responsive images (srcset)
   - Lazy loading below fold
   - Compress to <100KB per image

2. **Font Loading**
   - Font-display: swap
   - Preload critical fonts
   - Maximum 2 font families

3. **JavaScript**
   - Defer non-critical JS
   - Remove unused code
   - Code splitting for components

4. **CSS**
   - Critical CSS inline
   - Purge unused Tailwind classes
   - Minify and compress

### Mobile UX Patterns
```jsx
// Sticky TOC (Mobile)
<nav className="lg:sticky lg:top-20 lg:max-h-screen lg:overflow-y-auto">
  {/* Hidden on mobile, sticky on desktop */}
</nav>

// Collapsible Sections
<details className="group">
  <summary className="cursor-pointer touch-target">
    Expand Section +
  </summary>
  <div className="animate-slideDown">Content</div>
</details>

// Floating CTAs (Mobile Only)
<div className="fixed bottom-4 right-4 z-50 lg:hidden">
  <button className="bg-burgundy-600 text-white rounded-full p-4 shadow-xl">
    Save Guide
  </button>
</div>
```

