üö® CRITICAL RULES
CONTENT WRITING RULES (Blog Generator Standards)
Paragraph Structure:

‚úÖ 2-3 sentences maximum per paragraph (mobile-friendly)
‚úÖ One idea per paragraph
‚úÖ Transition words between paragraphs (30% of sentences)
‚úÖ Short sentences: 15-20 words average
‚úÖ Active voice: 80%+ of sentences
‚úÖ Vary sentence length (mix short & medium)

Readability Targets:

Flesch Reading Ease: 60-70 (8th-9th grade level)
Avoid jargon without explanation
Use conversational tone (not robotic)
Break complex ideas into steps
Use analogies for technical concepts

DO:
‚úÖ Use research-provided keywords naturally
‚úÖ Implement ALL 8 required schemas (JSON-LD only)
‚úÖ Test on real mobile devices
‚úÖ Follow Tailwind's CORE utility classes only
‚úÖ Optimize every image (<100KB hero, <80KB content)
‚úÖ Create accessible components (ARIA labels, keyboard nav)
‚úÖ Double-check all internal links (no 404s)
‚úÖ Use semantic HTML5 tags (<article>, <section>, <nav>)
‚úÖ Add loading states for async content
‚úÖ Include transition words (30%+ sentences)
‚úÖ Cite sources naturally in content
‚úÖ Update date prominently displayed
DON'T:
‚ùå Use localStorage/sessionStorage (not supported in Claude.ai)
‚ùå Use custom Tailwind classes (compiler unavailable)
‚ùå Exceed 10KB schema per page
‚ùå Markup invisible content in schema
‚ùå Use Microdata/RDFa (JSON-LD only)
‚ùå Ignore mobile breakpoints
‚ùå Hard-code content (use props/data)
‚ùå Skip alt text on images
‚ùå Create >4 nesting levels in components
‚ùå Keyword stuff (sacrifice readability)
‚ùå Use generic anchor text ("click here")

