### Color Palette (Tailwind Classes)
```
Primary: burgundy-600 (#8b1f42) - Main brand color
Accent: burgundy-700 (#cc2d5c) - Hover states, emphasis
Light: burgundy-50 - Backgrounds, soft highlights
Background: cream-100 (#fcfaf5) - Page background
Text Primary: gray-900 - Body text
Text Secondary: gray-600 - Muted text, captions
Border: cream-400 - Dividers, card borders
Success: green-500 - Positive actions, confirmations
Warning: amber-500 - Cautions, alerts
Error: red-500 - Errors, critical warnings
Info: blue-500 - Informational callouts
```

### Typography Scale
```
H1: text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold
H2: text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold
H3: text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-semibold
H4: text-xl md:text-2xl font-sans font-semibold
Body Large: text-lg leading-relaxed
Body: text-base leading-relaxed
Body Small: text-sm leading-relaxed
Caption: text-xs text-gray-500
```

### Spacing System
```
Section Padding: py-16 md:py-24
